OL,3,CWhat is the government's record on
OL,4,Ctackling Islamophobia?
OL,6,FThe Conservative Party has battled
OL,7,Fwith accusations of Islamophobia for
OL,8,Fyears, and the events over the weekend
OL,9,Fhave led many to ask whether the party
OL,10,Fis doing enough to tackle it.
OL,12,FAllegations of Islamophobia in the
OL,13,FConservative Party
OL,15,FIn 2016, Zac Goldsmith's London
OL,16,FMayoral campaign was repeatedly
OL,17,Faccused of being Islamophobic and
OL,18,Fsmearing Sadiq Khan. Mr Goldsmith
OL,19,Fdenied the claims at the time.
