OL,3,CWhat is the government's record on
OL,4,Ctackling Islamophobia?
OL,6,FIn 2018, Boris Johnson wrote a column
OL,7,Fcomparing Muslim women to
OL,8,F"letterboxes" and "bank robbers".
OL,10,FAt the time, Tell Mama - a group that
OL,11,Frecords Islamophobic hate incidents in
OL,12,Fthe UK, reported that in the week
OL,13,Fafter Mr Johnson's comments,
OL,14,FIslamophobic incidents rose by 375 per
OL,15,Fcent.
