OL,3,CWhat is the government's record on
OL,4,Ctackling Islamophobia?
OL,6,FIn 2018, the Muslim Council of Britain
OL,7,Fwrote to the Conservative Party
OL,8,Fcalling for an independent inquiry
OL,9,Fafter incidents of Islamophobia rose
OL,10,Fat a local level within the
OL,11,FConservative party.
OL,13,FThe MCB letter was supported by 350
OL,14,Fmosques across the UK.
OL,16,FIn 2019, then-Prime Minister Johnson,
OL,17,Fordered a report into Islamophobia
OL,18,Fwithin the party.
