OL,6,FThe report was published in 2021 and
OL,7,Fwhile it concluded that anti-Muslim
OL,8,Fviews were seen at local association
OL,9,Fand individual levels, it found no
OL,10,Fevidence of "institutional racism".
OL,12,FIt was met with criticism by
OL,13,FConservatives like Baroness Warsi,
OL,14,Fformer MEP Sajjad Karim who said the
OL,15,Finvestigation was too restrictive in
OL,16,Fits scope.
OL,18,FOther campaigners said Muslims had
OL,19,Fbeen excluded from the investigations.
