OL,3,CWhat is the government's record on
OL,4,Ctackling Islamophobia?
OL,6,FIn 2022, Conservative MP Nus Ghani
OL,7,Fsaid she was dismissed as a minister
OL,8,Fafter a government whip told her that
OL,9,Fher "Muslimness was raised as an
OL,10,Fissue", and her "Muslim woman minister
OL,11,Fstatus was making colleagues feel
OL,12,Funcomfortable".
OL,14,FChief whip Mark Spencer came forward
OL,15,Fas the person who spoke to Ms Ghani
OL,16,Fand said the allegations were untrue.
OL,17,FHe was later cleared of any misconduct.
