OL,3,CWhat is the government's record on
OL,4,Ctackling Islamophobia?
OL,6,FIn 2019, the all-party parliamentary
OL,7,Fgroup on British Muslims produced a
OL,8,Fworking definition of Islamophobia as
OL,9,Fbeing a "type of racism that targets
OL,10,Fexpressions of Muslimness or perceived
OL,11,FMuslimness."
OL,13,FHowever, at the time the Conservative
OL,14,FParty refused to adopt that definition.
OL,16,FOn Sunday, Business Secretary Kemi
OL,17,FBadenoch tweeted that Conservatives
OL,18,Fuse the term "anti-Muslim hatred"
OL,19,Finstead because of concerns that Islam
OL,20,Fcannot be properly criticised under
OL,21,Fthe more commonly used definition.
