OL,3,CWhat is the government's record on
OL,4,Ctackling Islamophobia?
OL,6,FShe said Labour's definition "creates
OL,7,Fblasphemy law via the back door".
OL,9,FThe prime minister's spokesperson told
OL,10,Freporters: "There are issues in
OL,11,Frelation to the APPG's definition of
OL,12,FIslamophobia, which conflates race
OL,13,Fwith religion, does not address
OL,14,Fsectarianism within Islam, and may
OL,15,Funintentionally undermine freedom of
OL,16,Fspeech.
OL,18,F"But ... we have always been clear
OL,19,Fthat this Government does not and will
OL,20,Fnot tolerate anti-Muslim hatred."
